high_descs:
Turn right go straight to the sofa  
Take the fork    from the table 
Turn left go straight turn right   go  to walk 
put  the fork in the  bowl 
take the  bowl   Turn left go straight turn right   go  to walk 
turn  around the  right  side  
place  on the bowl in the dining table
anns.task_desc: Take the fork    from the table and  place  on the bowl in the dining table

high_descs: Head towards the sofa in the hall.
Take the fork on the spoon in the bowl
Turn around the bowl on the sofa side.
Pick up the bowl with the fork on it.
Take the bowl with the spoon and turn around.
Go to the right side of the diningtable.
Put the spoon into the bowl on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the fork on the spoon put it in the bowl on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn right to see a tall lamp across the room, walk to it, then go left to the middle of a sofa on the opposite side of the room.
Pickup the fork from the sofa.
Take a step to the left side of the bowl.
Stick the fork inside the bowl on the sofa.
Pick up the bowl from the sofa.
Turn around and head to the middle of the diningtable's side that is on your left.
Place the bowl under the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the plate with the fork in or under the diningtable
